Why 17/25: Allstate has implemented several sustainable technologies and operational changes (renewable procurement via RECs, fleet hybridization, energy/real-estate efficiency measures, supply chain programs, biodiversity and sustainable agriculture investments). However, most interventions are established approaches (RECs/offsets, hybrid fleets, procurement policies) rather than multiple breakthrough technologies deployed at scale (e.g., on-site large renewable PPAs, proprietary carbon-capture or platform-level energy storage deployments). See supporting disclosures and program descriptions [allstate](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGE9ELnZL92u-ePIgnTTVK5XEK4rO_Cs4BoxtYAQ_7RSsgiXmctIsynJot6wrwAo2BS5CdiIJxE6vL9e7QciosmjDCE00qOVyqAbZNvU0mOae8N-fjYMVbNsYrDrwuyqat--QXvT_fXxEUuCt3ZC8loOgSQZruqltL0B9TNpgpGj5gASc_SP-yaqNgEJ41WTYneAtF-aSb3K_0uQLLiLW-fxqU=) [allstatecorporation](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUTtvMm_hiXU6EKX5rsSYbr2ZKkLFImxXdCMPcpXUA5YEQSK-YXS7YpXRmAE0Hyw161JBvKOsnfZmkSVgNkFcFvhw2CPC1I9g-M3zIaGqpnUfA-pNETRRxZXjLrcI66hSf5KIJn0ZrT9M0Og4sKTXWPGWKMcF-D1W0YXuSq3S7NvC3bipI-gufEttkrKYV0_en) [csrwindo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG0_i_X2Il0nAdTODEW4ZRtDPgIDjNSq4b0OYJOcmEHV1xEQb_CQtLTqEUItaskF46Zsx9AbE8BatoLwrb7XsFXSD48zH8vsQSQ6zS12_5OqQf-eWN548FDZqIBVt9wHN15HdIsgXJ-BmQ1R81XbWHPzL9AnC_wJgVAiQJJ0hr-HXWu-T_P-42rfPbGIflIyZSFembprPk=).

