Why 16/25: Allstate shows a strong innovation program orientation — venture funds, targeted climate investments, supplier and procurement programs, governance innovations and climate-policy development — but there is limited public evidence of proprietary sustainable-technology R&D, major patents, or industry-transforming pilot deployments (e.g., a large in-house tech platform or ownership of renewable generation assets at scale). The company is active in financing and partnering to scale solutions rather than being a clear proprietary-technology developer [allstateinvestments](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF2X9bI55bCYI_-GpleNuw1mPUTdwnurml_OWJe6nmLRx_bAVSS69xbzSVlnuwY2m9ie4un1CakO5NDpVsWy4PNjENCc_8T2e4m6KbJ1pNuyMvMbqlSFD90tjTQsD9cVVWRP3rYFJH2I1_mYTvzTpwKmRWx-T7U_hJCoaQ=) [globalventuring](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFNEX2oXKeQx5VYQdyk_sotrADSCpCb2CDnQ2Rjv-aNg7zNiUjLrgzDg_FZyXC0vdhswRnK7eZMVPBv3yVdDjXpu_oR2HW5Te6yeXkSrLaQfcMtrCSqUjkn4wr_TGGBtLDc2OPlZ3WRrt8limep7P-5xvZJj8yMMngnNYXBro1Ab_u2gp_onaVSC8U4H9Sdz5u-A9wctuh47lu_ZXXszaxU_7KDIQ9k26AknorafOlKuaG3Irr_Xywnz0U=) [allstate](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGE9ELnZL92u-ePIgnTTVK5XEK4rO_Cs4BoxtYAQ_7RSsgiXmctIsynJot6wrwAo2BS5CdiIJxE6vL9e7QciosmjDCE00qOVyqAbZNvU0mOae8N-fjYMVbNsYrDrwuyqat--QXvT_fXxEUuCt3ZC8loOgSQZruqltL0B9TNpgpGj5gASc_SP-yaqNgEJ41WTYneAtF-aSb3K_0uQLLiLW-fxqU=).

