- Relative strengths: Allstate is in the active group of insurers incorporating sustainability into business and capital allocation (sizable climate investments, public net-zero commitment, governance structures) [allstateinvestments](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF2X9bI55bCYI_-GpleNuw1mPUTdwnurml_OWJe6nmLRx_bAVSS69xbzSVlnuwY2m9ie4un1CakO5NDpVsWy4PNjENCc_8T2e4m6KbJ1pNuyMvMbqlSFD90tjTQsD9cVVWRP3rYFJH2I1_mYTvzTpwKmRWx-T7U_hJCoaQ=) [allstate](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGE9ELnZL92u-ePIgnTTVK5XEK4rO_Cs4BoxtYAQ_7RSsgiXmctIsynJot6wrwAo2BS5CdiIJxE6vL9e7QciosmjDCE00qOVyqAbZNvU0mOae8N-fjYMVbNsYrDrwuyqat--QXvT_fXxEUuCt3ZC8loOgSQZruqltL0B9TNpgpGj5gASc_SP-yaqNgEJ41WTYneAtF-aSb3K_0uQLLiLW-fxqU=).
